Dialogue: 9,0:21:35.53,0:21:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sena.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:40.20,0:21:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sena...
Dialogue: 9,0:21:42.80,0:21:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tui...
